by smnandre at 2024-01-30T13:47:08Z

:class="bar" may be invalid.... But on custom elements, class:="bar" is not ;)

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Hello</title>
</head>
<body>
<twig-bar class:="foo"></twig-bar>
</body>
</html>
```

This is perfectly valid HTML code ;)

